{"tid":1932880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人服退燒藥返港，入境後才到醫院求診","createTime":"2020-03-19T03:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T03:42:26.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f91acffbfc390ea7e697e20d5766f406ccdc64e5","tid":1932880,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，至今早，公立醫院已接收至少 10 名武漢肺炎病毒初步確診病人。<br />\n<br />\n大批港人，特別是留學生，嘗試趕在本港今日（ 19 日）凌晨對全球國家實施強制檢疫令前回港，面對大批自高危地區回港人士，衞生署曾估計會有大量輸入個案。有醫護人員亦表示，近日已接獲多宗自外地回港的懷疑個案，更說有人服退燒藥返港，入境後才到醫院求診。<br />\n<br />\n成架飛機玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc5d2332e2607d1eedebc6d6e63cdbf3da5f98c","tid":1932880,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"乜春防護衣都無撚用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3965f10143e08bdeb0c358edaf0cf89ac1f88b99","tid":1932880,"uid":80516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d9787d2880c4a8c0bef6218f0b9799593a581e","tid":1932880,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"醫護係時候罷工先, 有真普選先復工"},{"pid":"ba5b354e9a86e69e0499e1a416a59d0431511c0f","tid":1932880,"uid":276548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3965f10143e08bdeb0c358edaf0cf89ac1f88b99","tid":1932880,"uid":80516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"三毛畜賤最愛既臭蟲論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107469417131da70810317a3e79dd7262ce72677","tid":1